		<title>15Social Concerns in Bootle</title>
		<content> As an inner-city area within the      
 depressed North West the problems are 
 related to the economic situation.    
                                       
 Unemployment at all levels,but        
 especially the young,is very high     
 (70-80% on some estates).Deterioration
 in housing and social services has    
 produced a high level of urban        
 deprivation.                          
                                       
 This has engendered a feeling of      
 hopelessness and aimlessness and is   
 expressed in the high incidence of    
 drug and solvent abuse among the young
 and the high rate of crimes against   
 property.                             
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
